<SYNC Start=1017605><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1017850><P Class=ENCC>
"ls he gonna call me the next day?"<br>and "Where is this going?"
<SYNC Start=1021513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1022621><P Class=ENCC>
So he said he wanted to hold off<br>until he was prepared to be serious.
<SYNC Start=1027354><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1029528><P Class=ENCC>
