<SYNC Start=1038961><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1039204><P Class=ENCC>
If he wants to see me again, he can<br>call. If not, that's fine too.
<SYNC Start=1043004><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1043208><P Class=ENCC>
