<SYNC Start=1305769><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1310008><P Class=ENCC>
It's not as if you have<br>a boyfriend's shoulder to cry on.
<SYNC Start=1313466><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1315514><P Class=ENCC>
Well, no. But l....
<SYNC Start=1317141><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1317582><P Class=ENCC>
If it were me, I'd have difficulty<br>getting out of bed at all.
<SYNC Start=1321074><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1327426><P Class=ENCC>
You know, I try to stay positive.
<SYNC Start=1329917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1330595><P Class=ENCC>
So you....
<SYNC Start=1331892><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1332531><P Class=ENCC>
You feel like going for a run?
<SYNC Start=1334999><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1337736><P Class=ENCC>
